          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-4-1632217499558-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> coconut stock</strong> to the pan with 1 tsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong> and a generous pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to medium and cook for 4-5 min further or until the sauce has reduced slightly</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1632217503216-x200.jpg",
